Examples

 
library("breakDown")
library("randomForest")
HR_rf_model <- randomForest(status == "fired"~., data = HR, ntree = 100)
#> Warning: The response has five or fewer unique values.  Are you sure you want to do regression?
explainer_rf  <- explain(HR_rf_model, data = HR, y = HR$status == "fired")
mp_ex_rf <- model_performance(explainer_rf)
mp_ex_rf
#>         0%        10%        20%        30%        40%        50%        60% 
#> -0.8544274 -0.5072159 -0.3866740 -0.2835859  0.0943493  0.1293515  0.1625286 
#>        70%        80%        90%       100% 
#>  0.2091416  0.2840750  0.4041018  0.7574591 
plot(mp_ex_rf)
